          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "百姓雖有不善者，聖人化之使善也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 3
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "百姓德化，聖人為善",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "百姓為信，聖人因而信之。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 6,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "百姓為不信，聖人化之為信者也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 7,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 3
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "百姓德化，聖人以為信。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 8,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "聖人在天下怵怵常恐怖，富貴不敢驕奢。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-10",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言聖人為天下百姓混濁其心，若愚闇不通也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-11",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 10,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "注，用也。百姓皆用其耳目為聖人視聽也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-12",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "聖人愛念百姓如嬰孩赤子，長養之而不責望其報。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
